bmsapi_post_germplasm_search

bmsapi_post_germplasm_search.Rd

post a germplasm search. As compared to BrAPI implementation this call allows for incomplete search on names (starts with, ends with and contains)

Usage

bmsapi_post_germplasm_search(
  con = NULL,
  gids = "",
  nameFilter = NULL,
  page = 0,
  pageSize = 1000
)

Arguments

con

a brapriv2 connection object

gids

a vector of gids

nameFilter

see details

pageSize

Details

nameFilter is a list with two character components:

type

one of the following values : STARTSWITH, ENDSWITH, EXACTMATCH, CONTAINS.

value

the text string to search for
